Chaotic CHANGELOG

This document holds changes made to the library across different releases.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
 VERSION 1.01 (In Progress)
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Additions:

- Added CHANGELOG!!
- Added Window::setCursor() to control window cursor.
- Added generateEmbedded() function to generate the embedded_resources.cpp file.
  The function is disabled on release under the macro _INCLUDE_EMBEDDED_GENERATION.

Fixes:

- Fixed ImGui cursor flickering bug.
- Small change/fix on the Hopf Fibration Helper window inside chaotic_demo().
- Fixed frame-capturing bug that produced incorrect coloring on transparent object screenshots.